="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uFAv __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z" k-observe="" k-use="220ef652-25b0-4285-a354-edd881d69045" k-style="inlineStyles_235_5" k-class="mergedStyles_236_5" onclick="" k-init="" k-bound=""><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z"><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IY0d __P0nNOOvpt01x __HcWluv-7J"><div data-testid="mentions-inline" style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IY0d"><span class="aui-primitive __HcWWkUdHN __HcWNg-FAv __3LVrZoFAv">16&nbsp;clientes mencionan entretenimiento, 16 de forma positiva, 0 de forma negativa</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ"><span class="aui-primitive"><span class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">16&nbsp;clientes mencionan "Entretenimiento"</span></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __dChWb2ruQw4B __P0nNOOzO001x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">16&nbsp;positivas</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __dChF3jO2MCfBw4B __P0nNOOzO001x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">0&nbsp;negativas</span></div><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand=_92_29 k-id=52ca548e-b110-43b7-931d-79e5a9e37ff7 k-parent=f4c40e73-856d-43c8-99c3-7cdc369c7cda k-init k-ready--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-component=Pressable-vu7Dc6_viwy2yRr k-id=c5d5696f-8a46-42d9-a088-0b90d00066ab k-composed=Pressable_close_92_29 k-parent=52ca548e-b110-43b7-931d-79e5a9e37ff7 k-data=[omitted] k-init k-ready--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand-let=defaultStyles_36_5 k-parent=c5d5696f-8a46-42d9-a088-0b90d00066ab k-data=[omitted] k-init--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand-let=accessibilitySt_65_11 k-parent=c5d5696f-8a46-42d9-a088-0b90d00066ab k-data=[omitted] k-init--><button k-on-click="onPress_onGestu_72_54" aria-label="Cerrar" data-testid="close-button" style="border: none; background-color: transparent; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: inherit; font: inherit; border-radius: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWz_S8Xm" k-observe="" k-use="c5d5696f-8a46-42d9-a088-0b90d00066ab" k-aria-checked="tmpCoalesce_tmp_87_54" k-aria-selected="tmpCoalesce_tmp_88_55" k-style="inlineStyles_92_3" k-class="mergedStyles_93_3" onclick="" k-init="" k-bound=""><img src="./como_agua_para_chocolate_files/pi_button_close.png" k-metric-loaded-enabled="false" aria-hidden="true" style="display:inline-block;height:12px;width:12px;object-fit:cover;" class="aui-primitive __HcWIi-bS7X-z"></button><!-- k-injected k-component-close --><!-- k-injected k-component-close --></div><span data-testid="aspect-summary" class="aui-primitive __P0nNOOvpt01x __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">Los clientes consideran que el libro es emocionante e interesante. Mencionan que resulta bastante entretenido y emociona a los lectores. Destacan que siempre engancha y enseguida atrapa al lector.</span><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOKHIwIJ"><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-component=SnippetList-PNN7RVeHzV36aKU k-id=d69ba109-ece5-4759-9366-44c4ce78d41c k-composed=SnippetList_asp_110_25 k-parent=f4c40e73-856d-43c8-99c3-7cdc369c7cda k-data=[omitted] k-init k-ready--><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z"><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand=snippet_35_21 k-id=3c3c6438-529b-411a-9a44-ee030b58ef68 k-parent=d69ba109-ece5-4759-9366-44c4ce78d41c k-data=[omitted] k-init--><div style="" class="aui-primitive __HcW37uIi- __HcWIi-82IiB1 __HcWIi-bS7X-z __P0nNOOvpt01x"><div data-csa-c-type="uxElement" data-csa-c-item-id="cr-product-insights-cards_read-more-link" data-csa-c-pos="" data-csa-c-posx="" data-csa-c-posy="" data-csa-c-owner="CustomerReviews" data-csa-c-item-type="" data-csa-c-parent-element-id="" class="aui-primitive" data-csa-c-slot-id="cr-product-insights-cards_read-more-link" data-csa-c-id="9q0i1w-ctknmt-wpyvwh-3z4szw"><span class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ"><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">"</span><span class="aui-primitive"><span class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">Maravilloso. </span><span class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ __SARCET4AB">Muy interesante</span><span class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">, fácil de leer pero bien hecho. Una historia conmovedora. Me lo leí de una sentada y me encantó.</span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive __SAR2l0zNyyuZ">"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="aui-primitive"> </span><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-component=TextLink-WvGnR4tz_NonT_u k-id=61ac872a-8788-48ae-a1c1-2fbf1a7246ac k-data=[omitted] k-init k-ready--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-var-addr=/MainView_summar_97_5/BottomSheetCont_200_21/aspect_77_22/1/SnippetList_asp_110_25/snippet_35_21/0/TextLinkTemplat_56_25/mouseHover_37_11 k-expand-let=mouseHover_37_11 k-parent=61ac872a-8788-48ae-a1c1-2fbf1a7246ac k-data=[omitted] k-init--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand-let=hoverStyles_62_5 k-parent=61ac872a-8788-48ae-a1c1-2fbf1a7246ac k-data=[omitted] k-init--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-component=TextLink-NhgxjsMLgh3kZYe k-id=15419efd-ff07-4b48-9ea2-9ef246558f41 k-composed=TextLinkPrimiti_111_1 k-parent=61ac872a-8788-48ae-a1c1-2fbf1a7246ac k-data=[omitted] k-init k-ready--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-var-addr=/MainView_summar_97_5/BottomSheetCont_200_21/aspect_77_22/1/SnippetList_asp_110_25/snippet_35_21/0/TextLinkTemplat_56_25/TextLinkPrimiti_111_1/pressed_57_11 k-expand-let=pressed_57_11 k-parent=15419efd-ff07-4b48-9ea2-9ef246558f41 k-data=[omitted] k-init--><!-- k-injected k-decoded k-observe k-expand-let=useHref_72_5 k-parent=15419efd-ff07-4b48-9ea2-9ef246558f41 k-data=[omitted] k-init--><a href="https://www.amazon.es/gp/customer-reviews/R1UOSCBPYEOMZ5" target="_self" tabindex="0" data-testid="read-more" k-on-mousedown="pressed_onMouse_87_5" k-on-mouseup="pressed_onMouse_88_5" k-on-mouseenter="onMouseIn_89_32" k-on-mouseleave="onMouseOut_90_33" class="aui-primitive __SAR