ncios, promociones</li><li>Realizada a cambio de dinero en efectivo, descuentos</li></ul><div>Cuando recibamos tu informe, comprobaremos si la reseña cumple con las Normas de la comunidad. Si no es así, la eliminaremos.</div></span><div class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-report-abuse-confirmation-dialog-button-container_2vYw9" data-mix-operations="ConfirmReportAbuseClickHandler" data-mediatype="IMAGE"><span class="a-button a-button-base _Y3Itb_media-popover-report-abuse-confirmation-dialog-button_35f75 _Y3Itb_modal-button_y9ZUs" id="a-autoid-21"><span class="a-button-inner"><input type="submit" class="a-button-input" aria-labelledby="a-autoid-21-announce"><span class="a-button-text" aria-hidden="true" id="a-autoid-21-announce">Denunciar</span></span></span></div></div></div></span></span></button></span></div><div class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-review-container_1dLQH"><div class="a-section _Y3Itb_cr-media-popover-sidepanel-container_1EUvC"><div class="a-section a-spacing-small _Y3Itb_cr-media-popover-sidepanel-header-section_3TxI7 _Y3Itb_cr-media-popover-sidepanel-header-section-truncated_DITiq"><div data-reviewbind="ProfileBlock"><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="./como_agua_para_chocolate_files/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" style=""><noscript><img/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">Amazon Customer</span></div></a></div><div class="_Y3Itb_rating-and-profile-badges-container_348ae"><i data-reviewbind="Rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star-small a-star-small-5 a-spacing-top-micro _Y3Itb_rating-block_2mVHa"><span class="a-icon-alt">5 de 5&nbsp;estrellas</span></i><div class="aok-hidden" data-reviewbind="RatingAlt" data-multiple-starts-suffix="Estrellas" data-one-star-suffix="Estrella"></div><div data-reviewbind="ProfileBadge" class="_Y3Itb_profile-badges-container_k5lqb"></div></div><h5 lang="es-ES" data-reviewbind="ReviewTitle" class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-title_EX93d _Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-truncated-title_2w0Qj">Libro de segunda mano con 30 años y en perfecto estado, ha merecido la pena.</h5><div lang="es-ES" class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-text-with-gradient_3T4-j"><div data-reviewbind="ReviewText" class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-text_3MYCz _Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-truncated-text_3nfmo">Es de segunda mano, me ha costado 4 euros y venía en muy buen estado</div><div class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-container-gradient_1zm2j _Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-container-gradient-truncated_3zXR9"></div></div><div class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-text-expansion-section_2guev"><a data-mix-operations="expandTextClickHandler" data-mediatype="IMAGE" href="javascript:void(0)" aria-expanded="false" class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-see-more_1sipE" role="button"><span class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-icon_1dF4M"><i class="a-icon a-icon-expand a-icon-mini" role="presentation"></i></span><span class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-text_oEWO4"><span>Más</span></span></a><a data-mix-operations="hideTextClickHandler" data-mediatype="IMAGE" href="javascript:void(0)" aria-expanded="true" class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-see-less_1Hpji" role="button"><span class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-icon_1dF4M"><i class="a-icon a-icon-collapse a-icon-mini" role="presentation"></i></span><span class="_Y3Itb_cr-sidepanel-expander-text_oEWO4"><span>Ocultar</span></span></a></div><ul class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-thumbnail-image-container_1q_4Q" data-imagealttext="Imagen del cliente" data-reviewbind="ImageThumbnailsBlock"><li class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-list-item-style_1njtu"><button data-mediaid="61dfxuugI4L" data-thumbidx="0" class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-thumbnail-image-button_1vtKQ" data-mix-operations="thumbnailClickHandler" aria-pressed="false"><img alt="Imagen del cliente" src="./como_agua_para_chocolate_files/61dfxuugI4L.jpg" class="_Y3Itb_media-popover-thumbnail-image-view_3-Y40" height="80" width="80"></button></li></ul></d